    "extras": [
      "Delphi is the strongest classic-history add-on from Athens if you want one deep mainland excursion without changing hotels.",
      "Meteora deserves an overnight if you want sunrise monastery views instead of a long same-day return from Athens.",
      "Paros or Naxos are calmer swaps for Mykonos if you prefer beaches and tavernas over nightlife.",
      "Rhodes and Thessaloniki are easiest to stitch into an island trip with short domestic flights rather than long ferry chains.",
      "Book Acropolis timed entry, Santorini ferries and Delos boats a few days ahead in May to October."
    ],
